# Ent workspace layout

Cursor loads project MCP from the **workspace root** (the folder that contains `ent/`).

| Open | Active config |
|------|----------------|
| Workspace root | `.cursor/mcp.json` |
| `ent/` alone | Invalid for onboard — audit fails `core.workspace_open_mode` |

**Sync after template changes:**

```bash
node ent/tools/ent.mjs sync --workspace-root . --agent cursor
```

**Source of truth:** `ent/agent-adapters/` templates. Workspace `.cursor/` is generated.
